#: ../../source/functions/system_control/play_pause.md:1
msgid "Play/Pause"
msgstr "播放/暂停"

#: ../../source/functions/system_control/play_pause.md:3
msgid "**Windows only**"
msgstr "仅限 Windows"

#: ../../source/functions/system_control/play_pause.md:5
msgid ""
"The play/pause key allows you to quickly toggle media playback on your "
"system. When you press this key, it will send a play/pause command to "
"your currently active media application (such as music or video players),"
" switching between playback and pause states."
msgstr ""
"播放/暂停键允许您快速切换系统上的媒体播放。当您按下此键时，会向当前活跃的媒体应用（如音乐播放器或视频播放器）"
"发送播放/暂停指令，实现在播放和暂停状态之间的切换。"

#: ../../source/functions/system_control/play_pause.md:7
msgid ""
"This function only operates when FlexDesigner is running. If you need "
"play/pause functionality without FlexDesigner, you may use your system's "
"built-in media keys, but those may not always stay synchronized with the "
"Flexbar indicator."
msgstr ""
"该功能仅在 FlexDesigner 运行时有效。如果您需要在没有 FlexDesigner 的情况下使用播放/暂停功能，可以使用系统自带的媒体键，"
"但这些键可能无法与 Flexbar 指示器保持同步。"

#: ../../source/functions/system_control/play_pause.md:9
msgid "In the FlexDesigner"
msgstr "在 FlexDesigner"

#: ../../source/functions/system_control/play_pause.md:11
msgid ""
"Apart from standard appearance customization options, this key does not "
"have any additional settings in FlexDesigner."
msgstr ""
"除了标准的外观自定义选项外，该键在 FlexDesigner 中没有其他额外设置。"

#: ../../source/functions/system_control/play_pause.md:13
msgid "![20251023-123225](image/play_pause/20251023-123822.jpg)"
msgstr "![20251023-123225](image/play_pause/20251023-123822.jpg)"

#: ../../source/functions/system_control/play_pause.md:13
msgid "20251023-123225"
msgstr "20251023-123225"

#: ../../source/functions/system_control/play_pause.md:15
msgid "On the Flexbar"
msgstr "在 Flexbar"

#: ../../source/functions/system_control/play_pause.md:19
msgid ""
"Tap the play/pause key on the Flexbar to control playback in your media "
"application. If playback is paused or resumed by other means (such as "
"keyboard shortcuts or clicking in the media player), the Flexbar key will"
" update to show the correct play/pause state."
msgstr ""
"在 Flexbar 上点击播放/暂停键可控制媒体应用程序的播放。当通过其他方式（例如键盘快捷键或在媒体播放器内点击）"
"暂停或恢复播放时，Flexbar 按键也会更新显示正确的播放/暂停状态。"

#: ../../source/functions/system_control/play_pause.md:21
msgid "You can freely customize the appearance of the play and pause states."
msgstr "您可以自由自定义播放和暂停状态的外观。"
